雞湯，烤肉+生菜 呢兩樣唔錯"},{"pid":"13995e723a71e9a9879609774d4e1a5b33a55897","tid":55713,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:01:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc575054ef2d2d0c6b2de5edfc6ddb4851bccf8b","tid":55713,"uid":65185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過韓國<br />\n去果d所謂必食<br />\nd野真係極級難食<br />\n又大份 又多油又辣<br />\n咩鍋咩鍋難食到仆街<br />\n最斃係d肉好多都係媒媒地<br />\n我懷疑果邊肉好貴<br />\n香港正好多<br />\n韓國食物=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n韓國當地出產既牛肉係好貴<br />\n<br />\nbtw，d人成日話韓國吃牛貴，咩韓國無進口日本，美國牛既咩？<br />\n<br />\n係日本，2百幾蚊hkd可以吃到好高質既日式燒肉放題<br />\n<br />\n照計韓國如果入口日本牛既話，應該唔會好貴"},{"pid":"518949b2c5591f53d6bbefae0684edc91c8b6d75","tid":55713,"uid":24350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"部隊鍋，人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/130034_3d3c61047e696c954a73e24ecac6eb7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F130034_3d3c61047e696c954a73e24ecac6eb7b.jpg&h=a74dd1a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54d3459b7c8b724dcd57b8ce2ecf4114ec402600","tid":55713,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得人參雞湯，烤肉+生菜 呢兩樣唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前有段時間去左韓國公幹個零月<br />\nd野真係唔太岩食<br />\n<br />\n韓國果d大漿湯 伴飯 etc 全部同一隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人參雞算比較特色 但個人唔太喜歡<br />\n湯濡米無左濡米隻咬口真係唔太好食<br />\n<br />\n反而冷面我覺得唔錯"},{"pid":"dd0b0186999725bc671ddd5b1e38248449664e8d","tid":55713,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f65ad065f3d336e5cf105c20033c7ffe66477c1","tid":55713,"uid":56661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"就算去日本，星馬泰，台灣，中國都有野好食<br />\n但係韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcd43e886dad78bf36c86477c018d24bd36ffab","tid":55713,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"去左幾日日日冇啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b440f31d964e992180e464575f57987e1846219b","tid":55713,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"之前去韓國旅行<br />\n全程最好食既野係蘋果"},{"pid":"717e240f567c3fe2a61ebb5cdfdf1b939301c45e","tid":55713,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去過韓國<br />\n去果d所謂必食<br />\nd野真係極級難食<br />\n又大份 又多油又辣<br />\n咩鍋咩鍋難食到仆街<br />\n最斃係d肉好多都係媒媒地<br />\n我懷疑果邊肉好貴<br />\n香港正好多<br />\n韓國食物=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n韓國當地出產既牛肉係好貴<br />\n<br />\nbtw，d人成日話韓國吃牛貴，咩韓國無進口日本，美國牛既咩？<br />\n<br />\n係日本，2百幾蚊hkd可以吃到好高質既日式燒肉放題<br />\n<br />\n照計韓國如果入口日本牛既話，應該唔會好貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除咗雞， 豬牛都唔平， 50蚊只可以買到200g美國牛肉碎"}]}